The article features statements from various current and former members of Congress, as well as advocacy organizations, policy experts, and media commentators, expressing their support for Gina Haspel as the nominee for CIA Director. Many of them highlight her extensive experience, bipartisan support, and qualifications for the role. They emphasize her dedication to protecting national security and her ability to confront emerging threats. The media commentary also praises Haspel for her performance during the nomination hearing, describing her as composed, disciplined, and knowledgeable. Overall, the statements advocate for Haspel's swift confirmation as the first woman to lead the CIA.